{"tid":1579176,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】粵網民疑因轉發《願榮光歸香港》　涉尋釁滋事罪被拘","createTime":"2019-09-18T12:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T11:03:26.000Z","uid":193217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9645744c6fca8bf31a7b91e64dcd58a7539d2265","tid":1579176,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威浪潮持續升級，內地當局控制相關資訊在內地流通。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由亞洲電台》報道，廣州網民賴日福日前疑因在社交媒體上轉發《願榮光歸香港》歌曲，被警方以涉嫌尋釁滋事罪刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》是由香港網民創作，號稱是示威者的「軍歌」，連日來沙田、大埔、黃大仙、油塘等多區都有民眾舉行大合唱活動。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述賴日福的朋友透露，賴日福此前在網上發布江西家鄉風景的影片及圖片，並以《願榮光歸香港》作為背景音樂，結果就在周日（15日）從江西家鄉回來廣州後，在住處樓下被十多名警察拘捕，現時關押在越秀區看守所。賴日福的家人已於周一（16日）晚上接獲警方發出的拘留通知書。<br />\n<br />\n賴日福的朋友稱，當局此舉是要向其他民眾發出警告，以免香港的示威資訊傳入廣東省後，導致有人「有樣學樣」。賴日福的另一名朋友亦直言，賴日福的情況不樂觀，可能會被重判。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，賴日福本身經常關注香港民主運動，早前他曾因穿著印有「公民抗命」字樣以及多名維權人士頭像的衣服衫在街上抗議而被拘留，結果被警方要求簽署保證書，10月前不得到香港旅遊及發表任何敏感言論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLX8OKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLX8OKM.jpg&h=81f03737&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n可以肯定共狗當呢首係反佢地既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27369ab2e41c18bb94f44d4621b83a845534b3e","tid":1579176,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee4cc40a6544736be3cc5e518f5e13a0bcf1e9eb","tid":1579176,"uid":273637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:50:00.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646abb7d3c7a9031b85b09d187e3dd010df64089","tid":1579176,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"[援助] 前線義士唔單止要開飯，要gear，仲要&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a5825818af005df962c0e3b4144833c6d3f1bab","tid":1579176,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed59c70df111752799323a6d44097ba8a662d664","tid":1579176,"uid":58174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"所以話喺鬼國醒咗嘅人真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f44e89ee4fd2358f315097a086fa7c1090dfe6","tid":1579176,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"革命歌上傳  大陸<br />\n才是老共最怕的事"},{"pid":"dd9fce6ea9f26418edd6fb5c2f4be4efabdc9361","tid":1579176,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"抖你個陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c5a91eb84bd8f490aa2800ef6b0f665197ab9e","tid":1579176,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》香港電台 十大中文金曲 2019<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582707\" data-auto-link t